3#ifndef __NVKM_MM_H__
4#define __NVKM_MM_H__
5#include <core/os.h>
6
7struct nvkm_mm_node {
8 struct list_head nl_entry;
9 struct list_head fl_entry;
10 struct list_head rl_entry;
11
12#define NVKM_MM_HEAP_ANY 0x00
13 u8 heap;
14#define NVKM_MM_TYPE_NONE 0x00
15#define NVKM_MM_TYPE_HOLE 0xff
16 u8 type;
17 u32 offset;
18 u32 length;
19};
20
21struct nvkm_mm {
22 struct list_head nodes;
23 struct list_head free;
24
25 u32 block_size;
26 int heap_nodes;
27};
28
29static inline bool
30nvkm_mm_initialised(struct nvkm_mm *mm)
31{
32 return mm->heap_nodes;
33}
34
35int nvkm_mm_init(struct nvkm_mm *, u32 offset, u32 length, u32 block);
36int nvkm_mm_fini(struct nvkm_mm *);
37int nvkm_mm_head(struct nvkm_mm *, u8 heap, u8 type, u32 size_max,
38 u32 size_min, u32 align, struct nvkm_mm_node **);
39int nvkm_mm_tail(struct nvkm_mm *, u8 heap, u8 type, u32 size_max,
40 u32 size_min, u32 align, struct nvkm_mm_node **);
41void nvkm_mm_free(struct nvkm_mm *, struct nvkm_mm_node **);
42void nvkm_mm_dump(struct nvkm_mm *, const char *);
43#endif
